          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3.-1690355158170-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated cheddar</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to a pot with your <strong>cornflour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and gently cook over a medium-low heat, stirring frequently</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted and the sauce has thickened – this is your<strong> cheese sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4.-1690355162662-x200.jpg",
