            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 20 min, remove the dish[es] from the oven and add the<strong> halved Brussels sprouts</strong> and<strong> bacon lardons</strong></p><p>Drizzle with<strong> vegetable oil</strong> and return the dish[es] to the oven for a further 15 min or until the vegetables are cooked through and golden – this is your <strong>potato, bacon & sprouts traybake</strong></p>",
